text:
To be honest, I thought 3 was a load of crap. Especially after the masterpiece Grandia II was. 

The voices were horrible, the story left much to be desired, and the little battle cries were the worst I've ever heard. No, scratch that. Skies of Arcadia had worse battle cries that consisted of "Moons, give me strength!" , "Hyuuuuuuuuuurgh!" and "Generic Name of Move!" (I still love SoA, though.)

But, this is all in my opinion. 3 didn't live up to my expectations. ;_;
